    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}The number of shards in this log store. Default to 2. You can modify it by "Split" or "Merge" operations. [Refer to details](https://www.alibabacloud.com/help/doc-detail/28976.htm)
{{% /md %}}</dd></dl>
